2yM30ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=955d4c10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n3bNb9qFiMg</a><br />\nPentagon 個合約比咗中國人話事嘅公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nmicrochip implant:<br />\nA Military-Funded Biosensor Could Be the Future of Pandemic Detection<br />\n<a href=\"https://rb.gy/6a8cvn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frb.gy%2F6a8cvn&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=873fc697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rb.gy/6a8cvn</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">Why are pandemics so hard to stop? </span>Often it&rsquo;s because the disease moves faster than people can be tested for it. The Defense Department is helping to fund a new study to determine whether <span class=\"red\">an under-the-skin biosensor can help trackers keep up</span> &mdash; by detecting flu-like infections even before their symptoms begin to show. Its maker, Profusa, says the sensor is on track to try for FDA approval by early next year.<br />\n<br />\nThe sensor has two parts. <span class=\"red\">One is a 3mm string of hydrogel</span>, a material whose network of polymer chains is used in some contact lenses and other implants. Inserted under the skin with a syringe, the string includes a specially engineered molecule that sends a fluorescent signal outside of the body when the body begins to fight an infection. The other part is an electronic component attached to the skin. It sends light through the skin, detects the fluorescent signal and generates another signal that the wearer can send to a doctor, website, etc. It&rsquo;s like a blood lab on the skin that can pick up the body&rsquo;s response to illness before the presence of other symptoms, like coughing.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">hydrogel研究都係中國人係MIT帶嘅project</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KjpPnOy6cBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKjpPnOy6cBQ&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=a8851f79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KjpPnOy6cBQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBill Gates, WEF, 聯合國, 中國俄羅斯聯手建立緊new world order <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oz0PVu7ht2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOz0PVu7ht2Q&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=e173df3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oz0PVu7ht2Q</a>"},{"pid":"64810b72449dbe4873450b2632988bccdc278139","tid":2294854,"uid":251026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0215eca448e189c0c137154d7c2de25cca2de1de","tid":2294854,"uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T10:35:48.000Z","msg":"你都睇得出就係冇實際作用<br />\n係個social conditioning嘅過程嚟<br />\n<br />\n想取消social distancing, 就要 contact tracing + mandatory vaccination<br />\ncontact tracing + mandatory vaccination = microchip implant <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCovid1984 = contact tracing+mandatory vaccination<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n3bNb9qFiMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn3bNb9qFiMg&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=955d4c10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n3bNb9qFiMg</a><br />\nPentagon 個合約比咗中國人話事嘅公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nmicrochip implant:<br />\nA Military-Funded Biosensor Could Be the Future of Pandemic Detection<br />\n<a href=\"https://rb.gy/6a8cvn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frb.gy%2F6a8cvn&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM30ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=873fc697\" dat